            <h1 class="c-article-magazine-title" itemprop="headline">Daily briefing: ‘Living fossil’ coelacanths can live to 100</h1>

            <div class="u-clearfix">
                
                <div class="c-article-teaser-text">
                    Distinctive fish reach maturity around 50 and their pregnancies last at least 5 years. Plus, 100 years since the discovery of insulin and how our ancestors learned to love bread and beer.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
            <div class="c-article-author-list-container u-clearfix">
                <ul class="c-article-author-list js-etal-collapsed" data-etal="25" data-etal-small="3" data-test="authors-list" data-component-authors-activator="authors-list">
    
